    <div xml:id="PN310-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. poṉmuṭiyār.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="PN310">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>pālkoṇṭu maṭuppavu muṇṇā ṉākaliṟ</l>
<l>ceṟāa tōcciya ciṟukō lañciyō</l>
<l>ṭuyavoṭu varuntu maṉaṉē yiṉiyē</l>
<l>pukarniṟaṅ koṇṭa kaḷiṟaṭ ṭāṉāṉ</l>
<l>muṉṉāḷ vīḻnta vuravōr makaṉē</l>
<l>yuṉṉila ṉeṉṉum puṇṇoṉ ṟampu</l>
<l>māṉuḷai yaṉṉa kuṭumit</l>
<l>tōṉmicaik kiṭanta pullaṇa lōṉē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>[My] mind suffers in distress</l>
<l>with him who was afraid of the little stick I aimed without force</l>
<l>because he would not drink although I fed [him] with milk. Now,</l>
<l>he who did not cease killing elephant bulls that took on a mottled colour,</l>
<l>he the son of strong people who fell in earlier days,</l>
<l>with an arrow one with the wound of which he said “I won’t heed [it]”,</l>
<l>[his] shock of hair like a horse’s mane,</l>
<l>is the one [here] with a tawny beard who lies on [his] shield.</l>
</lg> 
    </div>
